<h1>Diagram 8 — Phase Timeline / Roadmap</h1>

<h2>Purpose</h2>
<p>
  Shows the seven implementation phases of the IEMS ERP project, what was delivered
  in each phase, and the current status as of the mid-semester report date.
</p>

<h2>Mermaid Source</h2>
<pre>
timeline
